inn1.comm: short of a length and angling into Strauss, tucked on the onside but straight to the fielder
outside off and swinging away, left alone for Dhoni behind the stumps
full on off and just smashed down the ground, top shot!
full on off, pushed to cover for a quick single
full on middle and off, defended
slightly short, cramped for room, tries to cut but misses
width on off, steered between point and gully for a single down to third man
outside off and left alone
outside off, left alone
shot! width outside off and he stands tall and cuts that past point, four!
better ball, fuller on middle and off, defended back to the bowler
full outside off, swinging away and left alone
that ball rose on him , bounced at his throat, he drops his hands and steals a single through point
short on leg, jumps and taps that to the onside, one run

gone! Banged in short, Sehwa just stands there and tries to pull, the ball lobs up in the air and high to mid-on who collects an easy catch! Rash shot, nothing in it really, and England get a vital breakthrough
full on middle and off, defended
full on off, swing too, left alone
good line, swinging into him on off, defended to the off side
and again, good line, short of a driving length on off, defended quickly
very good shout! shaping into Dravid, rapped on the pads, that was probably going down leg, good bowling though
again, bowling from wide of the crease, angled into Dravid who defends
edged and dropped! Full outside off, Dravid drives at it and the catch flies to slip and Owais Shah spills it! How costly will that prove! Kabir Ali isnt happy
on leg, tapped to the onside
Shot! Full on the pads and he easily works that through mid-wicket for four!
full onoff, watchfully played to point
similar ball, this time Dravid drops his hands on it and the ball races between slips and gully for four
short on middle and off, worked to mid-wicket for a single
full on off, square-driven past gully for a single, Gambhir retains the strike
bad ball, full on the pads, easily turned away for one
full on middle and off, driven right to mid-on
full on off, defended back to the bowler
dont bowl there! Full on middle and leg and Dravid just whips that through mid-wicket for four! Easy pickings for him
full  on middle and off, easily tapped to the onside and a quick single is called for, Ali runs across but gambhir is home, good running
full on off, driven straight but mid-off cuts it off
too short and he stands tall and pulls that over square leg for four, Dravid showing good aggression here, magnificent shot!
Good comeback! Full and swinging away, good position of the seam, Dravid just pokes at it and gets beaten
short and angling into the ribs, worked around the corner andthey steal a single
full and driven back to the bowler
short and he gets into position to pull, swivels and the ball gets stuck in the helmet grill, top edge and that must have hurt, struck on the eye
angling into the pads, worked around the corner for a single
full on middle and leg, Gambhir chips that back to the bowler who gets a hand to it but misses it, the ball races down the ground and they pick up two
not as full, on off, played back to the bowler
fuller, angling across him, played forward to point, thinks about the run but Dravid says no
angling into his ribs, turned to the onside but right to square leg
shorter and on off, goes for the cut but misses, Jones collects on the bounce
good ball, short of a length on off, played to covers
good ball to start off with, good length on off, left alone for the 'keeper
this one is full but swinging in, Dravid goes forward and gets an inside edge onto the pads
full outside off, left alone as the ball fairly rolls to Jones, very disconcerting bounce that
outside off, Dravid watches it and slaps that past a diving Collingwood at point for four, a dominant Dravid here
Flintoff adjusts his line and brings this one into Dravid who pushes to mid-on
short of a length, driven to covers off the backfoot
full on middle and off, driven to mid-on
maximum! What a shot! Banged in short, gets into position so quickly and hooks that miles in the air and over square leg! Terrific shot and his home crowd loves it!
Gambhir on fire! Overpitched on leg and easily whipped through mid-wicket for four!

Ali strikes back! Full, swinging away on off, Gambhir pokes at it - perhaps trying to run it down to third man - but succeeds in getting a thin edge through to a diving Jones! Good catch, good ball, unneccessary shot and Ali get a wicket! Gambhir gone after a positive start, India two down
very good ball, very good leave, that ball was pitched just outside off, swung in and the ball carries through to the 'keeper
good ball again, similar line and length and pushed to the off side, Ali comes good after getting smacked around initially
short on off, cut to Collingwood at backward point off the backfoot
drifting into the ribs, just tucked around the corner for a single
full on off, pushed back to the bowler who collects to his left
short and rising from middle to off, Yuvraj watches it carefully and leaves it
short of a length on off, tapped towards mid-off and calls for the single, harries down the pitch and gets it, well run
good ball, on off, defended to the offside

Gone! Huge wicket! Ali again! Short of a length outside off, Yuvraj plays a weak push and gets an inside edge onto the stumps! Loose shot and Ali gets another to his name! India slipping after a decent start, theyre three down now
good ball, rising from off, watchfully played to covers
full pitched, almost a yorker length, dug out back to Ali
short of a length on off, Kaif stands tall and punches back past the bowler and mid-on and gets a single, off the mark
Shot! Banged in short, uneven bounce sees the ball keep low but Dravid watched it all the way and short-arm jabs that over square leg for four! Wow!
Fuller and pushed towards mid-off
what a ball! Welcome to kaif! Flintoff brings one in and across him, swing beats Kaif's forward prod and Jones collects! Good stuff
slightly shorter and this time he gets behind it and defends
Full on middle and leg, a tad slower, turned to mid-wicket but yells 'NO' to his senior partner
full and angling in, Kaif defends and gets an outside edge down to third man
turned around the corner for one
again on the pads, easily worked past square leg for a double
full outside off, Dravid moves well forward and pushes to covers
on off again, played to point

RUN OUT! shorter on off, Dravid stands tall and pushes that past the bowler and calls for the run, mid-on springs across, picks the ball and hurls that back towards the striker's end, hits the stumps as Kaif dives to make his ground,  looked very, very close, third umpire called for and it appears kaif's bat was in the air, unfortunate dismissal but kaif has to go, India in deep trouble
good ball on off, watchfully defended off the backfoot, loud call of 'NO'
full on off, defended
pitched up outside off, driven right to cover
Extra bounce, Dravid stands tall and plays towards point
full and moving in, pushed back to Flintoff
not as full and on middle and off, tapped to the onside but no chance of a run given the last dismissal
similar ball, defended to the offside in a hurry, calls of 'NO' again
very good stuff this, again full right on off and Dravid can only defend back to Flintoff
much better, back on track, slightly shorter on off, Dravid forced to defend off the back foot, top over that from Flintoff
good ball on off, slower, Raina gets his head down and presents the full face of the bat, showing Anderson the make, well defended
again  on off, pushed to mid-off
Quicker and moving into him from around the wicket, Raina quickly behind the ball and defends
full on middle and leg, driven straight to mid-on
what a beauty! Pace and bounce beats Raina's backfoot defense, Anderson taking a cue from his captain
banged in short on off, Raina uppercuts but right to Blackwell at third man who parries the ball on the bounce and stops  four
from around the wicket, good lift but Raina right behind it, pushed to point
similar ball and still rising but well played to the cover region for a single
short outside off, Dravid doesnt time it well, cuts right to Collingwood at point
where did that come from? Swings well into Dravid who makes room to cut but the ball goes of this pads and rolls dangerously close to the stumps
full and driven right back to Flintoff who does well to stop it
good length on off, played to point
full and seaming away from off, Raina drives a long way away from his body and gets beaten
full on middle and off, played back to the bowler
on off, tries to cut but misses
short on middle and leg, turned right to square leg
short and seaming away on off, left alone for the 'keeper
full on middle and leg, turned straight to Pietersen at mid-wicket, good over this from Plunkett
welcome Collingwood! Short and wide on off, slow delivery, Dravid reaches for it and slaps that through covers for four!
better ball, quicker on off, played to cover
slow on off again, low bounce, Dravid leaves it alone
fuller on middle and off, well driven down to mid-off for a quick single
short of a length on off, delivered from around the stumps, pushed to cover
fullish on off, well punched between the bowler and mid-off, fielder dives and saves four, batsmen cross for one
good length delivery on off, quick too, Raina well behind the line and defends impressively
short on off, Dravid punches that but straight to cover-point, missed out on a freebie there
good ball, straight on off, Dravid manages to whip it to mid-wicket
similar ball, similar shot to mid-wicket who moves in a couple paces

Plunkett strikes! Full ball again on off, good line hes maintained all over, but the ball kept low and crashes into the base of middle and off, Dravid looks down and shakes his head as he walks off, sorry youve got to go, Plunkett all smiles, but the bounce has really been uneven all morning...India in disarray!
good ball, again that perfect offstump line, pushed to point, fine over
good ball on off, Raina well behind the line and pushes to mid-off
on the pads and easily turned around the corner for a single
very good shot, pitched up on off and he eases that past mid-off four four, good way to start proceedings for yourself!
poor ball, down leg, clips Pathans leg and runs fine for four, umpires calls wide though, runs anyway
full again, played to the off side
very wide outside off, called wide rightly and that gives the crowd something to make noise about
fuller on middle and leg, driven right to mid-on
short on off, goes for a weak cut but misses
full on middle and leg, clipped straight to mid-wicket
good rising ball on off, beats his forward defensive prod
good ball on off again, Raina can only guide that to point, tight line this from Plunkett
this one is brought into him, Raina gets his head down and defends
full again and he can only drive that to short mid-on, very good spell from Plunkettt
full on off, driven back down the ground, Ali gets a hand to it, well stopped
short outside off, Pathan went for it, called wide anyway
good shot, slightly short of a length on off but Pathan stands tall and punches that off the backfoot through covers for four, retrieval job for the fielder
outside off again, angling across Pathan from around the wicket, left alone
in the slot to be driven and he does, well timed too, had four written all over it but Pietersen at covers is superb, saves certain four
pitches on middle and leg, raps the pads, Ali appeals but that was going down
angling across him and seaming away, easily left alone by Pathan
great shot! overpitched, driven handsomely through covers for four
on off, guided to point
better length, on off, left alone for the 'keeper
wide down legside, Jones collects, poor ball that
on the pads, easily worked fine for a single
good ball on off, rising, poked at and gets the edge through gully for four, crowd wakes up!
full on middle and leg, driven to mid-on
flighted on middle and leg and turned to square leg
similar ball, turned again but to the fielder
on off and Raina advances, can only drive to cover
on middle and leg, turned to the fielder
tossed up,driven back to the bowler
wide down leg, blemish in an otherwise fine over
tossed up on leg, driven to mid-wicket, very good over from Blackwell
full on off, driven right to cover
short on middle and leg, hits the pads outside the line, ball rolls towards point
well bowled and well played, full on off, Pathan gets forward in defense
angling down leg, off the pads and around the corner for a single
majestic! Overpitched and Raina is down on one knee and free-strokes that through covers for a welcome boundary, breaks the shackles on that occasion, class from the young left-hander
on middle and off, played back to the bowler
tossed up on off, played to covers
shorter on off, goes to cut and gets an inside edge down to third man
tossed up on middle and leg, drives to mid-wicket who fields well and they have a mixup in the middle, safe in the end
tossed up again, prodded to the onside
tossed up, moves forward and punches between bowler and mid-on
tossed up on off, pushed back to the bowler
short on off, pushed to Collingwood at point, quick single called for as he throws the ball at the stumps, just in
short again, stands tall and cuts past point for a single, sweeper collects and throws it back in
great one there! Again short outside off and he jumps up and slaps that in the air over gully for four!
again on off, slightly slower, played to point, calls of 'NO'
better ball, fuller in length on off, Raina well forward in his defense
oooh, on off, swinging away, poked at and gets beaten
tossed up on middle and leg, turned to square leg
tossed up on off, invited the drive and he does, all the way to mid-off
on legs, worked to mid-wicket
shorter in length, played fine but no run
tossed up on off, Raina forward in defense
shorter and quicker, Raina can only get on the back foot and push to mid-on, tidy over again from Blackwell
full on off, driven straight to mid-off
on off again, pushed back past the bowler on the off and he wants one, they scamper and make it easily in the end
short on leg, swivels and pulls, doesnt connect well and the ball flies down to wide third man on the bounce, streaky shot from Raina
pitched up on off, driven through covers
angling away from middle and leg, easy pickings for a single on the onside
and again, same line and he works that easily into the mid-wicket region for another single
tossed up on middle and leg, goes for the sweep but doesnt connect well
flighted on the pads, flicked towards square leg who misfields
drifting down leg, lapped around the corner for a couple
tossed up on middle and off, goes for the sweep again, ball lobs up off his chest and rolls to the offside
on middle and leg, worked right to mid-on
fuller on middle and off, pushed to the left of Flintofff who moves across and stops
over steps, fuller on off, driven through covers for a single
fuller on off, pushed to covers
full on off leg and its turned down to line leg for one
overpitched outside off and he square-drives that past point and gully, Shah in the deep dives but carries the ball into the ropes with him
tossed up on off, advances, can only push to cover

Blackwell strikes! Tossed up on middle and leg, Raina advances again and tries to chip it over the infield but can only hit it to  Collingwood at wide mid-on, poor shot and the spinner is rewarded for a tidy spell, India in further trouble!
tossed up on middle and off, pushed back to the bowler
dropped short and Dhoni pulls through mid-wicket for one, off the mark
on middle and leg, worked to mid-wicket
tossed up again, driven to mid-on
bouncer outside off, Dhoni leaves it alone
short again, this time Dhoni drops the hands and guides it through gully for one
goes right through Pathan's forward prod, very good pace there from Flintoff, Jones misfields and they should have run a bye
fuller on off, driven past point for one
full and angling in from off, Dhoni goes forward and pushes back to Flintoff
full on off, driven past point for a single, Dhoni will keep the strike...to face Blackwell? Hmm...interesting....
tossed up on off, prodded to mid-off, no run there
played off the backfoot to Blackwell
fuller on off, Dhoni well forward and steals a single towards point
flatter trajectory, played back to the bowler
full on off, played to point for one
short on middle and leg, Dhoni rocks back and pushes that past square leg, runs hard and gets the second
full outside off, swish and miss to Jones behind the stumps

gone! Anderson pitches this one up on middle and off, Pathan tries to chip that done the ground - or somewhere, who knows judging by that weak shot - and the ball flies down towards mid-off where Plunkett dives forward and to his left and takes a very good catch. Not sure what Pathan was thinking there, useless shot really, should have stuck around, but hes gone and England make inroads into the Indian tail!
full on off, Harbhajan forward and drives to covers where Collingwood misfields and allow the single
full on middle and leg and worked easily to mid-wicket for a single
close! Full on off and Harbhajan drives in the air to cover, ball reaches the fielder on the bounce
angling into Harbhajan and drifting down leg, not called wide
short on off, Dhoni cuts and finds the hole in the cover region, gets one for that
flighted on off, Harbhajan forward in defense, not entirely convincing
again tossed up, this time his defense is much better and the crowd shows their appreciation
down leg and he laps that fine for a single
on the pads, worked around the corner but straight to the fielder who stops brilliantly
tossed up on middle and leg, Dhoni plays that awkwardly as only he can, ball rolls to the onside, another good over from Blackwell
angling down leg, Jones dives to his left and take a very good take, wide not called
On middle and leg, pushed to mid-on
Full on off, pushed back to the bowler
Full again, inside edge rolls to the offside
On the legs, worked to square leg for one
full on off, pushed back to the bowler
around the wicket not, and wide down leg side
full on off, played back to the bowler
tossed up on off and driven to mid-off for a single
short and Dhoni pulls that through mid-wicket for a single
shorter on off, Harbhajan stands tall and pushes to point
Blackwell drops it short and Harbhajan obliges with a slap through covers and point for one, England wont mind as he will retain the strike
full on off, played to the onside somehow
again full on off and Harbhajan gets forward and defends towards point, tidy stuff from the bowler
wow! that was pitched up in the slot and Harbhajan unleashes a fine drive ALL ALONG THE GROUND and down to long-off for four! Impressive Bhajji!
slightly shorter but Harbhajan is right behind that and defends off the back foot
full on middle and leg, worked to the onside
short again on off, Harbhajan stands tall and tries to take his bottom hand off it, outside edge runs down to third man, again he will retain strike
back to over the wicket, tossed up on legs, prodded to the onside
full on middle and off, pushed to the cover-midoff region and calls for the run, just makes it
down leg, gets some bat on it but to the fielder
fuller on leg, worked fine for a single
no run
good delivery and turned to backward square leg region
wide down leg, bad start from Ali, batsmen collect a run too
fuller on off, Harbhajan drives well through cover, Dhoni wants two and they get it comfortably
shorter, angling into him, manages to stand tall and work it the the onside
good length on off, Harbhajan awkwardly plays that to cover
fuller on middle and off, slower ball, not sure if Harbhajan picked it but he pushes to mid-on
full on middle and leg, picked up over short mid-wicket for two
banged in short and angling down leg, Harbhajan semi-pulls with one hand and the ball runs around the corner, they scamper through for one
tossed up on leg, well swept for two
tossed up on off, defended
similar ball, defended again
slower in the air, defended again to covers
fuller on off, pushed to midoff for a single
not as full, on middle and leg, Dhoni well forward in defense, very good spell from Blackwell, he only went for 25 from his 10, picked up Raina too
full on off, played straight to cover
massive! pitched up on middle and off, Harbhajan gets a foot forward and swings that high over long-on for six! Great shot to lift the pressure some!
swining into him, he goes for a sweep and the ball raps the pads, everyone appeals but that was going down leg
dropped short and Harbhajan jumps in the air and gets bat to it, the ball races down the legside for four!
fuller on middle and leg, easily pushed to mid-on for a single
good slower ball in the slot, Dhoni can only drive back to Plunkett
full on off, pushed back to the bowler, the angle from around the wicket working that time
perfect delivery, in the blockhole, he manages to dig it out and collect a single as the ball rolls behind him
slightly short on off, slower too, Dhoni punches towards point for one
full on middle and off from around the stumps, pushed to mid-on for one
full on middle and off, chipped past the bowler for a single to mid-on
bad ball down leg, very wide but Harbhajan manages to the finest bit of bat on that and he will get four more to his name! Good little innings this from Harbhajan, when will Dhoni step it up though?
very good delivery, in the blockhole, Dhoni digs it out and Plunkett fields
Dhoni comes to the party! Full ball on the legs, Dhoni whips that around the corner for his first boundary, 50-run stand up between these two!
good ball, change of pace, outside off, very slow, Dhoni gets down to cut but misses
full toss on leg stump, Dhoni gets down and slaps that over square leg for four! Very bad ball and treated with disdain by Dhoni
gone! Short ball outside off and Dhoni can only cut that to Collingwood at backward point, Plunkett gets a wicket and Dhoni's unusual innings comes to an end, India eight down now!
full ball on middle stump, well driven through covers for a single and off the mark immediately
full and in the blockhole, well dug out back to the bowler by RP
full toss again on off, drives and gets an outside edge down to third man

and Harbhajan goes too! Full ball outside off and he can drives that hard but straight to Flintoff and extra cover, Ali strikes yet again but Harbhajan played well for his 37, entertaining and vital knock for his side
And thats that! Full and a tad slower outside off, Sreesanth goes for it and can only lob that high in the air to Pietersen at extra cover, India all out for 203!

inn2.comm: Gone, Pathan strikes witha beauty! Perfectly pitched ball on off, Strauss looks to defend off the back foot but the ball kisses the edge and goes into Dhoni's hands! Big, big breakthrough and India are in this game!
no run
four
Another one! Pathan on fire! Pitched on middle and off and shapes in, catches Shah right in front of the stumps and England are 4 for 2! What a start to this innings! Fantastic stuff from Pathan!
full and swinging away outside off, left alone
full on middle and leg, worked to mid-on
on legs, worked to square leg
on off, poked at and gets four through slips and gully, edgy!
full on middle and off, pushed back to the bowler
good ball from over the wicket, on off and moving away, Pietersen shoulders arms
too far down the legside, wide called
very good ball again, rising from across the stumps and nips back to touch Pietersen's pads, but pitched outside line
no run
full again and Pietersen comes down the track and defends
full on off, Pietersen well forward in defense  and rapped on the pads, Pathan appeals but thats very optimistic
no run
full outside off, smashed through covers
good ball on off, Prior well forward in defense
again on off, driven to mid-off, Pathan keeping a good line
identical ball and its mistimed on the drive, ball rolls towards cover&
Well timed! This ball was straigther and Prior connects well, gets bat to ball and sends it screaming down the ground for four, good shot!
not as full, still on off and Prior goes back and defends to cover
better ball, pitched on middle and off and held its line, Prior forward in defense
short on off, played off the back foot towards cover-point, he wants the run and sprints down the pitch, Prior just makes it home at the other end, close call
full on off, defended and beats the bat, very close!
on the pads, whipped away to Gambhir at square leg who dives to his left and saves four, that ball was in the air but didnt carry
full on off, Prior drives and manages to squeeze the ball in the gap between point and gully and the ball races away for four, not where he wanted it to go but he will take it
full and in the blockhole, dug out on the bounce to mid-off
slower ball on off, low bounce and Prior pokes at it and gets beaten, Dhoni collects
short of a length on off, mistimes the back-foot drive to cover
fuller on middle and off, defended and gets an inside edge to square leg
shorter but the same line, Pietersen turns that to Sehwag at short mid-wicket
angling away from him on off, again that low bounce as Pietersen shoulders arms
fuller on middle and off, Pietersen comes down the track to hit it, gets struck on the pads, Pathan lets out a loud appeal but the umpires not interested, very tricky stuff this from Pietersen
top shot, full on the pads and Pietersen will hardly miss those, easily picks that up and sends it over square leg for four!
better ball, not as full on off, left alone with a stride forward
good ball, short of a driving length on off, some seam movement into Pietersen as he walks into that shot
similar ball and again Pietersen walks into the shot, flicking across the line and getting four through mid-wicket, top shot again from the big man
dropped shorter and Pietersen makes room to work in on the onside for a single
full on middle and leg, worked to mid-off and again shouts 'NO'
Oh shot! Comes down the pitch and works that through mid-wicket and mid-on for four more!
Yowza! Pathan drops short this time and Pietersen always saw that coming, stands tall and pulls that handsomely over mid-wicket for four more!
full and slower, Prior forward in defense
short of  a length on middle and off, defended off the back foot
wide outside off, Prior goes for it and fails to connect
fuller this time and punched towards cover
full on the pads, Pietersen was early into his stride, walks across this stumps and flicks that disdainfully over square leg for four!
better, slower and fuller on middle and off, watchfully played to mid-on
good ball! Held its line and rose as it passed Pietersen's forward prod, good ball to end an ordinary over
fuller on and around off, guided to Yuvraj at point
good ball on off, kept its line, Prior watchfully defends
on the pads, played to Sehwag at short mid-wicket, not in complete control of that shot
full and jagging in from middle, worked fine for a single
slower ball, well bowled, on middle and off, Pietersen pushes to Sehwag again
short again, Pietersen charges, lucky to get an inside edge off a hoik to square leg
full on off, firmly driven to Sehwag at mid-off
angling into the pads, worked to square leg, Yuvraj moves to his left and throws it back but Prior safe
Shot!Tossed up outside off, dragged from across the stumps for a four over mid-wicket
good ball, beats him in the drive

Bhajji strikes! Tossed up bravely on off again, Prior tries a repeat of that slog-sweep but can only hit it high to deep backward square leg where Gambhir holds his nerve against the glaring sun and hold a fine catch! India are fighting hard and furious! Harbhajan gets a wicket in his first over, good bowling change, great strike
no run
full on middle and off, pushed to mid-on
on middle and leg, worked through mid-wicket for a brace
fuller in length and Flintoff drives with one hand but gets enough on it to send the ball down the ground for four, brilliant!
on the legs, worked square
on the legs, eased around the corner for two more, erratic bowling this
good ball, drifter on off, Pietersen forward and gets beaten
another good ball, well forward in defense
tossed up, down the pitch and driven to mid-off for one
good placement, short on off and Flintoff easily works that past point, Pietersen pushes for the second
flatter on middle and off, pushed back to Harbhajan
tossed up and defended off the backfoot
full on the legs, easily flicked fine for a single
short outside off, left alone
full on off, goes for a slog and mistimes it through mid-on
short of a length, chopped into the ground and to cover on the bounce
full on off, pushed back to the bowler
tossed up, defended
tossed up on off, chipped down the ground to mid-on
Good shot! Tossed up one middle and leg and swept hard for four past square leg
and another! Full on off  and he dances down the track and lofts that down to long-off for four, Pietersen on fire
faster on middle and leg, worked fine to bat-pad
full on off, driven to the bowler
shaping away from middle to off , Flintoff shoulders arms
lucky! Full on off, Flintoff throws the bat at it one-handed, the ball goes high over cover-point and into the ropes for four
short and worked through covers
banged in short and he swats that JUST over mid-on for four more, Flintoff opening up
quicker and short on off, mistimed to cover
full on middle and leg, outside edge towards point for a single
tossed up, played back to the bowler
shorter, punched off the back foot to mid-on who misfields
short on off, uses the pace to guide that cheekily past gully for four, good shot!
full on middle and off, takes it and flicks across the line to mid-wicket who dives and saves runs
full on middle and leg, prodded towards mid-on
identical ball and this time he drives it just wide of mid-on for a quick single
close! Pitched up and Pietersen mistimes a drive in the air and it falls just short of mid-off
Majestic! Pitched up and he stands tall and lofts that straight back down the ground for six, what a fantastic shot! 100 up for England, 99 to get!
no run
full again and its chipped down to long-off for four
better ball, not as full and pushed back to Sreesanth
Wow! Wow! Going, going, you heard it -- GONE!! Full on middle and leg and he awesomely flicks that high over deep mid-wicket for another big six! Theres no stopping this man Freddie! What a shot!
one run
on legs, worked to mid-on
no run
full and pushed to mid-on
gone! Full toss on middle and leg, slogged high but right into Gambhir's hands on the deep midwicket ropes, well held and this match is not over yet! Pietersen departs, another big strike for India!
